data.description: No need for Flood Insurance! New roof! Newer AC, under warranty. Don’t miss out on this 2/2 pool home situated on an oversized double corner lot in a tranquil neighborhood. Experience the inviting open layout with a well-designed split  bedroom floor plan. The kitchen and family room provide a seamless connection to the screened room,  expansive lanai, and pool area – a private beach oasis right at home. Large heated pool and hot tub. Ample space for  entertaining is a highlight, with a spacious kitchen and a master bedroom featuring a walk-in closet and a  generous master bath. Enjoy the convenient shed, with electric, for storing your toys. With plenty of space, you can even  consider adding a second garage or utilize the extra room for boat or RV parking! RV electrical hook-up in the electrical panel too! Come see Englewood, Florida with its charming coastal vibes, serene beaches, and a laid-back atmosphere. The allure lies in the beautiful natural surroundings, including the stunning Gulf Coast beaches like Boca Grande and Englewood Beach. An  abundance of outdoor activities, such as boating, fishing, and exploring nearby nature preserves. Our friendly  community, diverse dining options, and proximity to cultural attractions also make it a favorite place to call  home. It's the perfect blend of relaxation and recreation, creating a memorable experience for those who enjoy  the Florida lifestyle.
